{
  "stem": "7684.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We changed our name to Chaim's mother's, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then he went away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We need to live.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had no money.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Chaim went to other-- other towns where the Germans moved away.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bought shoe laces.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't know what he bought.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really was so involved in my own misery that-- he bought things, and then came back and sold it in our area.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And-- and so-- so he was away a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and, and one-- he was not away, then I felt that I had-- I got the baby.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When I felt that I had-- I didn't know how-- if you have pain in the back, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I didn't know anything how to get a baby.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, I got pain in my stomach, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we had to walk five miles.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we came to a school.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was-- there was-- all Germans were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, there was no German-- were Polish doctors were with the Germans.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were very antisemitic in Poland.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Anyway, I was five days and five nights in labor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't look at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they didn't want to know anything about me, and if-- because I had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I still had the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted-- The farmer didn't buy enough ointment so that it-- there is an ointment when you put it on enough that it-- that you kill these germs.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So, so they didn't want to know anything about me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was laying there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "There were Polish women, but I couldn't speak with them.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They told me that I had to push and push and push.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they told me-- but they speak Polish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I didn't speak a word Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So finally, the head was showing.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
